# Always Rules for AICostPlanner

## Project Identity

AICostPlanner is a static cost-intent acquisition site. It is NOT AI API Ops. It is NOT LinkAI. It is NOT AI API Doctor. It is NOT aiapiprice.com. It is NOT AI API Radar.

## Critical Constraints

1. **No backend** - Static site only
2. **No database** - No user data
3. **No payment** - Routes to RutaAPI only
4. **No scraping** - Educational content only
5. **No cross-project contamination** - Never link to other projects

## Allowed External CTAs

- Primary: `https://app.rutaapi.com/register?lng=en`
- Secondary: `https://app.rutaapi.com/pricing`

## Prohibited

- Any link to: LinkAI, AI API Doctor, aiapiprice.com, AI API Radar, SellerFixHub, ExtensionFixes, guides.link-ai.cc, api1.link-ai.cc, aiapidoctor.com
- Claims: cheapest, lowest price, guaranteed compatible, all models available, unlimited usage, no billing risk, official partner
- Exact pricing claims (unless verified live)

## Safe Wording

- "check live pricing"
- "pricing can change"
- "model availability varies"
- "test small before scaling"
- "educational purposes"
- "not affiliated with [provider]"

## Design Direction

Agent Budget Console V2:
- Dark hero (near-black background)
- Light content sections
- Restrained accent colors (cyan/blue/green only)
- Monospace for technical labels only
- No purple gradients
- No cyberpunk excess

## SEO Requirements

- Unique title/meta/H1 per page
- Canonical URL (absolute)
- AI Summary block per page
- FAQ per page
- Last updated date
- Internal links

## Before Every Edit

1. Confirm this is AICostPlanner
2. Check AGENTS.md and PROJECT_MEMORY.md
3. Run `npm run validate:claims` after changes
4. Never add cross-project links
